title: 140: The Target Mealtime Food Finds Episode
itunes:title: The Target Mealtime Food Finds Episode
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are trying some great meals and meal starters from Target, like cauliflower-crust veggie pizza, buffalo chicken, a really yummy quinoa bowl, a veggie stir-fry kit, vegan cheese, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a new flavor of The Laughing Cow cheese that’s a HOMERUN! So stop what you’re doing, push play, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We’re going back to Target, but this time it’s all about meals, and boy did we find some amazing stuff to try!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
